a prominent family has demanded 
floggings for four religious policemen who they say forced their 
daughters car off the road and roughed up the 20yearold student 
because they believed she was dressed immodestly 
the incident is one of several indicating the rising tension 
between westernized saudis and islamic conservatives 
the conservatives are reasserting their control one saudi 
diplomat said on condition of anonymity issues that link religion 
and politics are highly sensitive in the kingdom and no sources 
wanted to be quoted by name 
the rigid moslems say they are enforcing islamic laws as 
founding prophet mohammed would have wanted they are especially 
vigilant in enforcing the ban on alcohol and socializing between 
the sexes as well as enforcing modest dress for women which they 
interpret as headtotoe covering 
formally known as committees for encouraging virture and 
preventing vice the police are usually called muttawiin or 
volunteers they reject wearing bands around their headscarves as 
many saudis do as unnecessary adornment they wear short thobes 
as the saudi mens robe is called and some carrylong thin camel 
prods 
the sources said the government concentrating its forces on the 
confrontation with iraqi president saddam hussein does not want 
tension over social issues 
in this kind of environment the last thing the ruling family 
